01:00:13.690 --> 01:00:17.020
The people around you supporting
you, saying, "You can do it.

01:00:17.020 --> 01:00:18.320
You can do it."

01:00:18.320 --> 01:00:21.820
And that's one of the most
important things that we can give

01:00:21.820 --> 01:00:27.440
to young people and adults
as well because I believe

01:00:27.440 --> 01:00:33.930 position:56%
in lifelong education, that
curiosity is through an entire life.

01:00:33.930 --> 01:00:36.690
And even if you don't
think you have the talent

01:00:36.690 --> 01:00:39.010
to do this thing, just try.

01:00:39.010 --> 01:00:40.800
Just try. Go out and do it.

01:00:40.800 --> 01:00:42.550
It's amazing what it will open up.

01:00:42.550 --> 01:00:45.600
CARLA HAYDEN: And to
