musical notes, they heard music

01:01:14.370 --> 01:01:17.570
and when I looked at
text, I heard words.

01:01:17.570 --> 01:01:18.870
And that was ok.

01:01:18.870 --> 01:01:24.420
And then I went off with
words and appreciated it.

01:01:24.420 --> 01:01:25.940
But, to know.

01:01:25.940 --> 01:01:29.800 position:56%
Sometimes you drive in neighborhoods
and you look on corners

01:01:29.800 --> 01:01:32.620
and you see people and you say wow,

01:01:32.620 --> 01:01:35.550
when did the light
go out in their eyes?

01:01:35.550 --> 01:01:38.470
When was that 4 year old
not given that chance

01:01:38.470 --> 01:01:39.920
to do that and here they are.

01:01:39.920 --> 01:01:43.020
DEBORAH RUTTER: That's the
spiral that is so difficult.

01:01:43.020 --> 01:01:46.760
That if you get into that, if you
