organizations in regard to hiring

01:02:33.200 --> 01:02:35.920
or promoting or just
generally creating a pipeline

01:02:35.920 --> 01:02:42.450
so that arts leadership may be
more inclusive to women of color?

01:02:42.450 --> 01:02:46.420
DEBORAH RUTTER: Well, first
of all you have to have,

01:02:46.420 --> 01:02:51.520
you have to be very explicit
in saying this is a priority

01:02:51.520 --> 01:02:56.860
and having broad ownership,
because if just one person owns it,

01:02:56.860 --> 01:02:59.360
it won't, it can't succeed.

01:02:59.360 --> 01:03:03.200
But, if you can get broad ownership
throughout your institution.

01:03:03.200 --> 01:03:06.790 position:56%
In my case, it was extremely helpful

01:03:06.790 --> 01:03:10.790
that the board was
right there with me.

01:03:10.790 --> 01:03:15.570
If not perhaps ahead of me
when I came to the Center

01:03:15.570 --> 01:03:18.290
and therefore putting
the structure in place.

01:03:18.290 --> 01:03:21.910
It does though mean that you
have to put mandates in place.

01:03:21.910 --> 01:03:27.290
And so for us now, there can
never be a final candidate pool

01:03:27.290 --> 01:03:31.160
that doesn't have diversity
in the pool.

01:03:31.160 --> 01:03:36.530 position:56%
And a conversation that always takes
place both from the hiring people.

01:03:36.530 --> 01:03:39.010
Now I'm lucky because
I have an institution

01:03:39.010 --> 01:03:44.510
that has really great reach and I
want to use the size and the reach

01:03:44.510 --> 01:03:49.550
of this institution to help build
as many future leaders as possible.

01:03:49.550 --> 01:03:52.520
But, I believe it can happen
in any kind of organization.

01:03:52.520 --> 01:03:56.170
It has to be something that
you believe as a core value.

01:03:56.170 --> 01:03:59.750
And you have to have the whole
team doing the same thing.

01:03:59.750 --> 01:04:02.450
Because the one person isn't
doing all of the hiring.

01:04:02.450 --> 01:04:04.440
There are a lot of
people doing the hiring,

01:04:04.440 --> 01:04:08.250
