01:04:08.250 --> 01:04:10.430
because there are jobs everywhere.

01:04:10.430 --> 01:04:15.360
It's not just in sort of the
administrative aspect of it.

01:04:15.360 --> 01:04:17.440
There are jobs throughout
our buildings

01:04:17.440 --> 01:04:20.090
that are supporting
the arts and are a way

01:04:20.090 --> 01:04:24.660
into our organization MARIN ALSOP:
We're looking also to trying

01:04:24.660 --> 01:04:27.600
to create diversity on
our board of directors.

01:04:27.600 --> 01:04:33.680 position:56%
I'm sure everyone, the good thing is
