01:06:11.340 --> 01:06:14.620
That's one of the most
diverse in the United States -

01:06:14.620 --> 01:06:17.480
one of the top ones in theaters.

01:06:17.480 --> 01:06:21.640
And that's something that
we work on on a daily basis.

01:06:21.640 --> 01:06:23.660
Our staff is diverse.

01:06:23.660 --> 01:06:25.910
Our programming is diverse.

01:06:25.910 --> 01:06:28.530
Our board is becoming more diverse.

01:06:28.530 --> 01:06:33.800 position:56%
